{"tid":1854183,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"GATWICK退唔到稅可以點","createTime":"2020-01-31T10:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T15:53:55.000Z","uid":292274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76e0394bcf45fc74c6a004c4d2d1b6bb541b51d6","tid":1854183,"uid":292274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"前幾日係gatwick返香港，入去離境之前已經問埋security check d保安confirm入到去有得退稅，點知入到去佢成間tax refund counter閂左，淨係痴左張notice話會三月先開返，而家得返出面先有得搞退稅，問左幾個機場既人佢地都話無野可以幫到我手，淨係叫我返黎寫email投訴，但我覺得成功率好低。想問下我而家飛多轉返去搞返個退稅會唔會大機會d，d稅絕對多過我飛返轉頭既機票價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：帶住完全唔識英文既屋企人去，入左離境先發現佢無開，當時行李已寄艙，無得即時決定買另一張機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e16769e31f03166b98976a46f38bf92586b106","tid":1854183,"uid":170591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"攞埋貨去領事館搞"},{"pid":"bf165d48966563fb98f161804c828887796ed440","tid":1854183,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"英國真係好撚流<br />\n成日都係咁撚樣<br />\n寫email去退稅公司講吧"},{"pid":"c3bdcc1bda54bfc60cbf9991e086c4479e919cc4","tid":1854183,"uid":292274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e16769e31f03166b98976a46f38bf92586b106","tid":1854183,"uid":170591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"攞埋貨去領事館搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"我有部分野係其他EU國家買，而家歐都脫埋，搵領事館既話都唔知佢地理唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b10bffce1a0ec92d204a15eb7e3fd9d521c886","tid":1854183,"uid":292274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf165d48966563fb98f161804c828887796ed440","tid":1854183,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"英國真係好撚流<br />\n成日都係咁撚樣<br />\n寫email去退稅公司講吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"係咪有成功